				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2019 19:18:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Elogee FishTruck</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4037075</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The image that was used in this article is non-compliant with the SCP wiki's license (CC BY-SA 3.0) as it comes from the EADS, a division of the Airbus corporation, as seen <a href="http://www.asdnews.com/news-17202/urlrewritetitle">here</a>, with no indication it has been released under Creative Commons. Thus, the image has been removed.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
