				<wikidot:authorName>tomode</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1376016</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It's cool but the picture of the man in what is clearly a standard RAF uniform really throws me off. Maybe Yankees dress their air techs differently but anyone from these British Isles could spot that uniform a mile off.<br /> Conversely SCP's without pictures bug me too, so I'd just have a radar readout with a single blip. Not exactly interesting but accurate.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
